    <h3>&ldquo;She&rsquo;s  Falling&rdquo; &ndash; Original Song Dedicated to Memory of Phoebe Prince </h3>
    <p>Hayley writes &ldquo;<em>To me, &ldquo;She&rsquo;s  Falling&rdquo; is about not knowing how to help someone who you can see is falling  apart</em>.&rdquo; Although Hayley&rsquo;s song was written about a girl she knew  personally, she, like all of us, was moved by the&nbsp; story of Phoebe  Prince,&nbsp; a 15 year old Irish immigrant attending school in Massachusetts,  who after months of being subjected to bullying from her peers, committed  suicide on January 14, 2010</p>
